html:
I’m sorry Rainbow
We know it’s not day one
I’m sorry Flower
This stuff just happens
So I yell into void
And there is no echo
Absolute emptiness
It’s like I have to
Acts full of shame
Is all I got
They say it’s hell
For what I done
I hurt myself
This isn’t healthy
That’s what I’ve learnt
So I am faulty
title: Faulty
